==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flash point
<hw>Flash" point`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the
lowest temperature at which the vapors given off by a volatile liquid
exposed to air will burst into flame when approached by a flame. Also
called <altname><cref>flashing point</cref></altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That point in time or that degree of provocation at
which someone will suddenly begin to act vigorously; -- often used in
reference to angry reactions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flashy</ent>⟦br⟧
